            <p>
                AS3Commons-reflect is an open-source library providing a reflection API for 
                ActionScript 3.0. Being a pure actionscript library it can be used for any
                Flash/Flex/AIR project.
            </p>
            
            <p>
            	The library provides clean, easy and complete introspection on class variables,
            	accessors, methods, metadata etc. etc. by parsing the xml returned by 
            	<code>flash.utils.describeType</code>. Parsing results are cached so that
            	possibly resource expensive parsing won't occur next time for the same class.
            </p>
            
            <p>
            	The library is thoroughly tested and is being intensively used for the
            	<a href="http://www.springactionscript.org/">Spring Actionscript</a> project.
            </p>
